# Wave2 M1 — sprint-memo compaction

Worktree: `/Users/martin/Downloads/Cursor tests/worktrees/cursor-m1-memo-compact`, branch `cursor/m1-memo-compact`, base 535e03f.

Goal: shrink `docs/sprint-memos/` retained codex log size. Wave1 archive added 9.8MB of raw logs (12 logs averaging 800KB). Trim to <2MB total per sprint while preserving all DONE-line evidence + last 200 lines of each codex run.

# Required reading
1. `docs/sprint-memos/SCAFFOLD.md` (if exists; else `docs/sprint-memos/`).
2. `docs/sprint-memos/7h-43-44-45-wave1/` directory (22 artifacts).
3. LESSON `[orchestration][archive-codex-artifacts]` 7h-39.

# Hard requirements
1. For each `codex-*.log` in `docs/sprint-memos/7h-43-44-45-wave1/`:
   - Extract first 30 lines (codex preamble) + last 200 lines (final output + DONE line).
   - Replace `<original.log>` with `<original.log.compact>` (or rename in-place to `.log` after deleting raw).
   - Preserve unchanged: all `*.prompt.md` files (they're already small).
2. Add `docs/sprint-memos/7h-43-44-45-wave1/INDEX.md` listing each artifact with: codex slug, marker state, DONE/FAIL line, original log size → compact size.

